   fix_r2 is a tool to fix the GRIB grid definition section (GDS) 
of the monthly means from the NCEP/DOE Reanalysis.


		Compiling fix_r2

1) get the gribw library & sample programs from

	ftp://wesley.wwb.noaa.gov/pub/gribw.tar

2) untar the library

	$ tar -xvf gribw.tar

3) cd to the tar directory

	$ cd gribw

4) make the gribw library

	$ make -f gribwlib.make

5) cd to the tools directory

	$ cd tools

6) make fix_r2

	$ make -f fix_r2.make


		Usage

$ fix_r2 old_grib_file new_grib_file

